{"tid":1737900,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭:將每日評估區會選舉可能性","createTime":"2019-11-19T05:39:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T06:50:01.000Z","uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f11eba5c6dd29bde78c8c4fc586d1144b72a5498","tid":1737900,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:39:16.000Z","msg":"近日本港示威衝突升級，社會關注區議會選舉能否如期於24日舉行。特首林鄭月娥出席行政會議前表示，政府仍然希望舉辦選舉，但選舉須公平公正，安全有序進行，主導權不在特區政府，而在使用暴力威嚇的人手上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，當局今日仍在評估選舉情況，或許未來每日都需要作出評估。目前只可以強烈呼籲所有人共同努力，停止暴力威嚇、堵路或破壞交通工具，否則兩萬名票站人員無法抵達票站，根本難以舉辦選舉。<br />\n<br />\n到時更加要阻止藍絲親友投票！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaea3d42b755942f6b77df638394559ebd3e8373","tid":1737900,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:40:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\n【行動】Twitter 戰線：世界各地政要火力全開！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入----------&gt; <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfL32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=2d55cd05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"045456a07ccfe73722196586df432308a0a74a5c","tid":1737900,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:40:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />撤左死全家<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔撤落地獄"},{"pid":"1b169188aa90a5ca93b337cb2aeb6bc9890cd9eb","tid":1737900,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:41:07.000Z","msg":"白痴林鄭選用區選威脅香港人<br />\nSorry I don't fucking care假民主選舉<br />\n連查冊都禁埋既種票偽選舉"},{"pid":"3bdff0ea0dba8ff3f1962e037d44